### [UC-AUTH-01] POST /auth/signup — 이메일 회원가입 (미구현)

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "홍길동",
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "serviceAgree": true
}

###

### [UC-AUTH-02] POST /auth/login — 이메일 로그인 (미구현)

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

> {% client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.data.accessToken); client.global.set("refreshToken", response.body.data.refreshToken); %}

###

### [UC-AUTH-02b] POST /auth/oauth/kakao — Kakao OAuth 소셜 로그인 (구현 완료)

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/oauth/kakao
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oauthId": "123456789",
  "name": "민서",
  "profileImage": "https://k.kakaocdn.net/example.jpg",
  "email": "kakao@example.com"
}

> {% client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.data.accessToken); client.global.set("refreshToken", response.body.data.refreshToken); client.global.set("userId", response.body.data.user.id); %}

###

### [UC-AUTH-02b] POST /auth/oauth/kakao — 신규 가입 케이스 (isNewUser: true)

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/oauth/kakao
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oauthId": "1999888777",
  "name": "신규카카오",
  "profileImage": null,
  "email": "new-kakao2@example.com"
}

###

### [UC-AUTH-02b] POST /auth/oauth/{provider} — 지원하지 않는 provider (에러: 400 예상)

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/oauth/naver
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "kakaoId": "123456789",
  "nickname": "네이버사용자",
  "profileImage": null,
  "email": "naver@example.com"
}

###

### [UC-AUTH-02b] POST /auth/oauth/kakao — 필수 필드 누락 (에러: 400 예상)

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/oauth/kakao
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "필드누락",
  "email": "missing@example.com"
}

###

### [UC-AUTH-03] POST /auth/token/refresh — 토큰 재발급

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

> {% client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.data.accessToken); %}

###

### POST /auth/logout — 로그아웃

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/logout
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###
